      <title>土耳其归还沙特数十亿美元资金 标志着经济复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/turkish-central-bank-set-to-return-5-billion-saudi-deposit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行迈出了具有里程碑意义的一步，归还了沙特阿拉伯 50 亿美元的存款，表明当局有信心能够在不承担富裕盟友债务的情况下恢复外汇储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/turkish-central-bank-set-to-return-5-billion-saudi-deposit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 07:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
